安装L4CAsADi(Learning 4 CasADi Framework)  github home page: https://github.com/Tim-Salzmann/l4casadi

pip install (CPU version):
pip install torch>=2.0 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu
ensure:setuptools>=68.1 scikit-build>=0.17 cmake>=3.27 ninja>=1.11
pip install l4casadi --no-build-isolation

from source (CPU version):
clone the repository(需指定clone路径 cd \d PATH): git clone https://github.com/Tim-Salzmann/l4casadi.git
All build dependencies installed via: pip install -r requirements_build.txt
Build from source: pip install . --no-build-isolation
(The --no-build-isolation flag is required for L4CasADi to find and link against the installed PyTorch.)

还未尝试CUDA加速：
GPU(CUDA)
CUDA installation requires nvcc to be installed which is part of the CUDA toolkit,安装CUDA的完整步骤：
1,  cmd-> nvidia-smi, 记录CUDA Version:12.3
2,  访问CUDA Toolkit Archive(https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-toolkit-archive)选择与PyTorch版本兼容的CUDA版本
3,  安装CUDA Toolkit
4,  配置环境变量,检查系统环境变量PATH中是否包含：C:\Program Files\NVIDIA GPU Computing Toolkit\CUDA\v12.3\bin C:\Program Files\NVIDIA GPU Computing Toolkit\CUDA\v12.3\libnvvp 
5,  验证安装：cmd-> nvcc -V
6,  CUDA安装完成后还需安装匹配CUDA版本的PyTorch：pip install torch==2.4.0 torchvision==0.19.0 torchaudio==2.4.0 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121
7,  验证PyTorch是否使用GPU：
import torch
print(torch.__version__)
print(torch.cuda.is_available())  # 应为 True
print(torch.cuda.get_device_name(0))
8,  make sure "nvcc -V" can be executed and run 
pip install l4casadi --no-build-isolation     Or
CUDACXX=<PATH_TO_NVCC> pip install . --no-build-isolation   
